<taxonomicName authorityName="Fleming" authorityYear="1821" box="[583,698,764,789]" class="Insecta" family="Leiodidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="295" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Leiodidae</taxonomicName>
, and one of the collectors of the 
<typeStatus box="[1063,1111,764,788]" pageId="4" pageNumber="295">type</typeStatus>
specimen.
</paragraph>
